oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Tennessee State Rally
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Automobile rallies; Tennessee State Fair; Festivals; Tippin, Aaron; Little Texas (Musical group); Opryland Hotel (Nashville, Tenn.);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and orange on white) announcing the 2005 Tennessee State HOG Reilly, a motorcycle festival with live music by Aaron Tippin, Little Texas, and the Renegades of Southern Rock at the Nashville Opryland Hotel on June 16-18. Poster features a metal photoplate of the Tennessee State Fair trademark.
